# Alert Management

## Role Purpose
The bot runs 24/7. Alerts are the only way to know something needs human attention at 3 AM. This skill defines what triggers an alert, how urgent each alert is, where it routes, and how to keep alert volume low enough that every alert still gets taken seriously.

## Alert Taxonomy
```
CRITICAL  → Page immediately, any time of day or night
            Human must respond within 5 minutes.
            Reserve for: financial risk, security, bot is blind

WARNING   → Notify promptly, human should check within 30 minutes
            Does not require waking anyone up.
            Reserve for: degraded performance, approaching limits

INFO      → Daily digest only, no immediate action required
            Reserve for: operational summaries, health stats

RESOLVED  → Automatic clear when condition resolves
            Always send a RESOLVED when a CRITICAL or WARNING clears
```

